# 10 Best Date Night Ideas in Victoria BC for 2026 (Active & Adventurous)

![10 Best Date Night Ideas in Victoria BC for 2026](/images/10-best-date-night-ideas-in-victoria-bc-for-2026.png)

Dinner and a movie is fine. But fine doesn't make a great story. If you want a date night in Victoria BC that you'll actually talk about the next morning, you need something that gets your heart rate up, sparks a little friendly competition, and gives you both something to laugh about.

Victoria has more to offer than you might expect. Here are 10 of the best options for 2026, ranked by how much fun you're actually going to have.

